{"tid":882550,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 – 南乳煎雞翼","createTime":"2018-10-30T08:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T06:54:31.000Z","uid":30742,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"74a027597d1281f7a7ccfcce7024711b1f70eba6","tid":882550,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GqPqpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GqPqpG.jpg&h=00ee8f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/t_t_YVX3phY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ft_t_YVX3phY&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=9321e831\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/t_t_YVX3phY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞翼其實係我冰箱萬年常備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只要諗唔到煮咩就係佢！ <br />\n煎、焗、炒、燜樣樣得！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢次就做一個終極簡單的南乳煎雞翼<br />\n醃、撲粉、煎&hellip;&hellip;咁就得左！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加碟菜半個鐘就食得！ 快過你打電話叫外賣！<br />\n唔好再出街食飯喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <br />\n南乳煎雞翼: <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/chicken-wings-with-red-fermented.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fchicken-wings-with-red-fermented.html&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d35a7965\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/10/chicken-wings-with-red-fermented.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b14d3bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=328ac19a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=nXiuCq19S5s3zIm%2Bc6BWl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c43574ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"fe1122c21cd9d014a82a8291af649118e358b22b","tid":882550,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"雞翼我鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3deffbac1230af0344307d9e02fb05766c08c792","tid":882550,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"老娘一定要支持"},{"pid":"f48fb18f66ee102c97d85f9233735fd112b12df1","tid":882550,"uid":121286,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"南乳唔係唔好食，係衰在焗或煎易搶火整燶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae3bdecc65210fa1a286b873f772eedfeaff924","tid":882550,"uid":8048,"